&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span class="caps"&gt;APPENDIX&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1) Compile older libnfs&amp;nbsp;library&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the beginning, I did not install the latest libnfs package. I ran into some issue while doing the&amp;nbsp;compilation. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Need to add &lt;code&gt;-I/home/fitbranded/include&lt;/code&gt; to&amp;nbsp;Makefile&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
