&lt;p&gt;3) &lt;span class="caps"&gt;GNU&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Autotools&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;libnfs packages requires &lt;span class="caps"&gt;GNU&lt;/span&gt; Autotools. If you want to know more about it, you can refer to the following&amp;nbsp;resources.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://bbs.archlinux.org/viewtopic.php?id=161452"&gt;ArchLinux&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;/li&gt;
